assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Super Telecom Co.,Ltd, together with its subsidiaries, provides communications technology services in China. It provides communication network construction, communication network maintenance, communication network optimization, software, and leasing and construction services, as well as equipment; and Internet of Things solutions for customers in various industries, such as water affairs, logistics, electricity, transportation, gas, fire protection, retail, and medical. The company is also involved in intelligent hardware manufacturing, which includes intelligent modules used to connect the perception layer and network layer of the Internet of Things used for Internet transmission; and smart operation of the city, including covering police affairs, urban management, and software and hardware solutions for fire, medical, transportation, water, energy, and other industries. In addition, it provides computer room construction, operation and maintenance services to operators or customers; and edge computing and IDC services for government, financial, Internet, and other customers; and comprehensive information technology (IT), such as communication technology, IT technology, AI technology, cloud computing, big data, etc., as well as new energy services. The company was formerly known as GuangDong Super Telecom Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Super Telecom Co.,Ltd in May 2019. Super Telecom Co.,Ltd was incorporated in 1998 and is based in Guangzhou, China.
